Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭 堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.96,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}無一例外都是異常數值
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.29,0:00:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這樣是無法搞清楚病因的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒有別的診斷手段嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從沒有見過龍族的治療記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漢娜 按住她的尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.01,0:00:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然嘗試了各種回復魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是都沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.55,0:01:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}藥草和調和藥劑之類也完全沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭 能聽見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.85,0:01:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.26,0:01:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們檢查了身體的每一個部位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也沒有發現明顯的外傷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.11,0:01:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會不會是龍族特有的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.98,0:01:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 你總是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以後小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:01:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我從圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.03,0:02:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拿了些可能有幫助的書過來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.46,0:02:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是適用哥布林的醫書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.51,0:02:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這本是關於爬蟲類生態的書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}露 這本書是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是禁止學生閱讀的禁書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.25,0:02:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}禁書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.64,0:02:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}我告訴圖書館的人說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.38,0:02:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}古蕾婭學姐的現在的身體狀況很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.69,0:02:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}前台的人借給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.61,0:02:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今天到底是誰在前台工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.99,0:02:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算這樣 這種書又是從哪裡弄來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.65,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家 古蕾婭拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.96,0:02:41.29,Default,,500,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:41.63,Default,,0,700,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安學姐到底去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐怕是去古代禁忌書庫了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}禁忌？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.45,0:04:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭學姐燒得好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.38,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看看 讓我檢查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.60,0:05:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}漢娜 準備為她降低體溫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.48,0:05:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.69,0:05:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事的 沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.54,0:06:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這裡是…圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:37.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看來是無意間走了近路 公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你去收集這些東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.34,0:06:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}石碑上寫了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然還有一些未能解讀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.15,0:06:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}還剩下…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼可能有龍鱗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.49,0:07:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}你醒了嗎 古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你沒事吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}古蕾婭學姐 古蕾婭學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.42,0:07:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.83,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回答我 古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.48,0:07:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.77,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古…古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}咦 安？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:39.96,Default,,0,600,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.27,0:08:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安 古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:42.29,Default,,700,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.10,0:08:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎麼了 安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.90,0:08:49.64,Default,,700,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}你沒事真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}話說 這裡是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:52.38,Default,,0,200,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}笨蛋 笨蛋 擔心死我了 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以先讓我穿上衣服嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}蛻皮？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 在我長大的過程中發生過幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}畢竟頭髮也變長了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.19,0:09:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欸呀 難道說胸也變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那種事…好像是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原來放著不管就可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.80,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}為我做了那麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.01,0:09:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒事沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}雖然最終也沒能幫上什麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}早知道這樣 還不如一直陪著色氣撩人的古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有那麼誇張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.88,0:10:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.15,0:10:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那可真的是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.46,0:10:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你手裡拿著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}沒…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.72,0:10:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}這是 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}作為我們成長的證明 我覺得應該保存下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笨蛋安
