Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭 把鹽巴給我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尾巴？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.12,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 是鹽巴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.29,0:12:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.07,0:12:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今天沒怎麼吃啊 古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.23,0:12:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 不好好吃飯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭剛剛…蛻完皮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:13:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}會營養不良的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.73,0:13:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}算了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}騙你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不會有錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.20,0:13:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尾巴變強壯了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.19,0:13:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古蕾婭
